    {
      "para_id": "Q001986.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninisina , his lady , Enlil-bani , the shepherd , who makes everything abundant for Nibru , the farmer of Urim’s plentiful barley , who purifies all divine powers of Eridug , the beloved en - priest of Unug , the powerful king , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the spouse choosen in the heart by Inana , built the E-urĝira ."
    }
  ],
